	    </ul>
	    <li> <u>Exercise 9.17</u> </li>
	    <li> <u>Exercise 9.14</u> </li>
	    <ul>
		<li>Add to your set of responses from <a href="http://8ball.ofb.net/answers.html">here</a>.</li>
	    </ul>
	</ol>
